title: 'Boys and Girl - Tyron Smith Done for the Year; Daniel Jeremiah Talks Dallas Defensive Effort; Week 5 Giants Preview
itunes:title: 'Boys and Girl - Tyron Smith Done for the Year; Daniel Jeremiah Talks Dallas Defensive Effort; Week 5 Giants Preview
description:
On today’s episode of the 'Boys and Girl Podcast, Jane and Bobby react to the news that Tyron Smith will miss the rest of the season. Plus, Daniel Jeremiah from NFL Network stops by to explain why he sees a lack of effort from the Cowboys defense. Also, Paul Schwartz from the NY Post stops by to preview the Giants. Follow Jane and Bobby on Twitter and subscribe to get all the latest inside information from two of the most connected people in the Cowboys’ community.
